alance v2.24.1] Normal dungeons Lv.21–50 gradual farm ease: smoother post-tutorial curve, more XP and gear drops for leveling.",logBalanceV2240:"[Fix v2.24.0] Fragment recombine bulk craft caps by equip bag space to prevent failed crafts.",logBalanceV2239:"[Fix v2.23.9] All craft recipes support bulk synthesis; 2s craft cooldown prevents anti-cheat rollback.",logBalanceV2238:"[Balance v2.23.8] Dungeons up to Lv.20 are much easier; new accounts get starter recovery needles and the first normal run resupplies.",logStarterHerb:"[Starter] Low Recovery Needles supplied. Good luck!",logBalanceV2237:"[Fix v2.23.7] Version update no longer blocks on cache or stale server version; settings show synced cloud account when connected.",logBalanceV2236:"[Fix v2.23.6] Save level rollback fix: login and cloud sync pick the highest-level save from account history.",logBalanceV2235:"[Fix v2.23.5] Fragment recombine crafts now land in visible bag slots; bulk synth no longer loses items.",logBalanceV2234:"[Update v2.23.4] Main/off-hand attack buttons only show in combat; profile combat stats use one decimal.",logBalanceV2233:"[Fix v2.23.3] Equip bag ghost slots from equipped duplicates/invalid entries no longer consume capacity.",equipBagFilteredEmpty:"Filter active — no matching gear in bag.",logBalanceV2232:"[Fix v2.23.2] Mandatory update reload now bypasses browser cache.",logBalanceV2231:"[Fix v2.23.1] Restored equip bulk-recycle helpers so the equipment panel renders again.",logBalanceV2230:"[Balance v2.23.0] Craft station XP from crafting; fragment recombine epic/hidden rates match monsters (weapon crate decoder keeps special boost).",logBalanceV2220:"[Balance v2.22.0] Craft tier fragments: recombine, advanced recycle, legendary/hidden craft.",logBalanceV2210:"[Balance v2.21.0] Fragment economy: lower recycle yield, boosted craft rarity, rare advanced fragment drops.",logBalanceV2195:"[Feature v2.18.36] Bulk recycle picker: select-all button and long-press drag to paint-select.",