d equip bag at bottom.'}},{version:'2.18.19',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'聊天室左側大頭像、右側完整 Lv.100／名稱／訊息，連續發言各自完整顯示。',en:'Chat: large left avatar; full Lv/name/message on right per send.'}},{version:'2.18.18',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'優化聊天室 Lv.100 整段等級字級與頭像貼合對齊，修正等級字體 CSS 錯誤。',en:'Tune full Lv.100 label size to align with chat avatar; fix level font-size CSS typo.'}},{version:'2.18.17',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'修復聊天室無頭像時顯示黑塊：改為 [ ] 占位符並修正頭像壓縮底色。',en:'Fix chat black avatar placeholder; show [ ] when no avatar; fix JPEG compress fill.'}},{version:'2.18.16',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'修復聊天室無法查看其他玩家頭貼：訊息附帶壓縮頭像並於聊天列表與個人頁顯示。',en:'Fix chat avatars: attach compressed avatar to messages; show in list and profile.'}},{version:'2.18.15',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'修復聊天室長按查看玩家個人頁無法完整滾動檢視的問題。',en:'Fix chat long-press player profile overlay scroll and full view.'}},{version:'2.18.14',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.14 開發者帳號自動發放全部既有與新增物品各 100 件，並支援雲端同步。',en:'v2.18.14 dev account auto-grants 100 for all existing and new items with cloud sync.'}},{version:'2.18.13',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.13 修復首次通關地城通關次數顯示為 2 的問題。',en:'v2.18.13 fix first dungeon clear showing count as 2.'}},{version:'2.18.12',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.12 已完成地城列表內已通關次數整段綠色修正。',en:'v2.18.12 fix green clear count in completed dungeon list.'}},{version:'2.18.11',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.11 已通關次數標籤與數字皆綠色。',en:'v2.18.11 clear count label and number both green.'}},{version:'2.18.10',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.10 已完成地城收合按鈕綠色顯示。',en:'v2.18.10 completed dungeons toggle in green.'}},{version:'2.18.9',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.9 地城通關顯示：已通關次數: 標籤＋綠色數字。',en:'v2.18.9 dungeon clear: Cleared: label + green count.'}},{version:'2.18.8',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.8 地城通關文案：已通關 (次數) 綠色、可挑戰 白色。',en:'v2.18.8 dungeon labels: Cleared (count) green, Available white.'}},{version:'2.18.7',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.7 地城已完成（次數）統一綠色顯示。',en:'v2.18.7 dungeon completed count shown in green everywhere.'}},{version:'2.18.6',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.6 地城難度頁：各難度顯示已通關次數（綠）或可挑戰（白）。',en:'v2.18.6 dungeon difficulty page: clear count (green) or Available (white) per tier.'}},{version:'2.18.5',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.5 反作弊修復：地下城進行中不回滾整張地圖，避免擊殺後怪物復活。',en:'v2.18.5 anti-cheat fix: no full dungeon map rollback mid-run; prevents monster restore.'}},{version:'2.18.4',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.4 擊殺怪物修復：同步地圖敵人 HP、多路徑定位清空格、擊殺後立即存檔。',en:'v2.18.4 monster kill fix: sync map enemy HP, multi-fallback cell clear, save on kill.'}},{version:'2.18.3',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.3 地下城移動錨定修復：同步清除舊格 @、戰鬥後重繪、新路徑從當前格出發。',en:'v2.18.3 dungeon move anchor fix: clear stale @, repaint after combat, path from current tile.'}},{version:'2.18.2',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.2 擊殺怪物後強制清空地圖格：依敵人引用定位、標記已完成格、防止怪物殘留。',en:'v2.18.2 cleared monster cells after kill: enemy ref lookup, completed tile flag, no monster residue.'}},{version:'2.18.1',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.1 地下城移動／戰鬥修復：尋路中斷、存檔錨定、擊敗格顯示、進入地城狀態重置。',en:'v2.18.1 dungeon move/combat fixes: path interrupt, save anchor, cleared tiles, entry state reset.'}},{version:'2.18.0',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.18.0 地下城點擊任意格自動尋路：最短路徑、每格 0.25 秒、僅踩怪物觸發戰鬥、經過出口不離開。',en:'v2.18.0 tap any cell to path: shortest route, 0.25s per tile, combat on monster only, pass exit without leaving.'}},{version:'2.17.9',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.9 防作弊系統：執行期狀態封印、裝備／天賦驗證、異常自動回復上次合法存檔。',en:'v2.17.9 anti-cheat: runtime state seal, equipment/talent validation, auto-rollback on tamper.'}},{version:'2.17.8',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.8 實機測試修復：版本提示不阻擋操作、離線可註冊本機帳號、開發帳號等級顯示與重複日誌。',en:'v2.17.8 audit fixes: non-blocking version notice, offline local registration, dev level flash and duplicate log.'}},{version:'2.17.7',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.7 地下城效能優化：地圖增量渲染、戰鬥 UI 快取、地城內延後雲端同步與存檔。',en:'v2.17.7 dungeon perf: incremental map, battle UI cache, deferred cloud sync/save in dungeon.'}},{version:'2.17.6',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.6 修復等級歸零與跨裝置登入：防雲端覆寫、啟動拉取進度、強化合併與上傳保護。',en:'v2.17.6 fix level rollback and cross-device login: anti-wipe upload, boot cloud pull, merge guards.'}},{version:'2.17.5',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.5 伺服器強化與加載優化：非阻塞啟動、預連線、延遲載入 Stripe/Gun、背景伺服器預熱。',en:'v2.17.5 server strengthen + load optimize: non-blocking boot, preconnect, lazy Stripe/Gun, background warmup.'}},{version:'2.17.4',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.4 修復 v2.17.3 啟動時雲端同步狀態初始化崩潰，設定畫面可正確顯示同步狀態。',en:'v2.17.4 fix v2.17.3 boot crash in cloud sync detail; settings show correct status.'}},{version:'2.17.3',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.3 修復設定內雲端同步誤顯示「本地存檔」；已登入帳號正確顯示同步狀態。',en:'v2.17.3 fix cloud sync status in settings showing local-only when logged in.'}},{version:'2.17.2',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.2 伺服器全面檢查：Bug 監測本地目錄備援、停止付款雜訊回報、Gun 節點優化。',en:'v2.17.2 server audit: local bug catalog fallback, payment noise filter, Gun peers.'}},{version:'2.17.1',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.1 Bug 監測修復：雲端同步未捕獲錯誤、中繼探測與分類優化。',en:'v2.17.1 bug-monitor fixes: cloud sync promise handling, relay probes, triage.'}},{version:'2.17.0',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.17.0 版本統一：部署後自動同步 version.json 至伺服器，強制所有玩家使用同一遊戲版本；雲端存檔標記版本。',en:'v2.17.0 unified version: deploy writes version.json; all players must run the same game version; cloud saves tagged.'}},{version:'2.16.0',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.16.0 雲端同步強化：每 2 秒自動同步、本地進度強制上傳、設定內狀態說明即時更新；修復離線誤報。',en:'v2.16.0 cloud sync: auto-sync every 2s, force-upload local saves, live settings status; fix false offline.'}},{version:'2.15.0',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.15.0 Bug 生命週期流水線：自動偵測、回報與伺服器健康檢查。',en:'v2.15.0 bug lifecycle pipeline: auto-detect, report, and server health probes.'}},{version:'2.14.3',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.14.3 修復等級異常回調；強化經驗進度保存與雲端合併。',en:'v2.14.3 fix level rollback; improve XP progress save and cloud merge.'}},{version:'2.14.2',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.14.2 新手教學更新：貼合純手動硬核與地城教學。',en:'v2.14.2 tutorial refresh for manual hardcore and dungeon guide.'}},{version:'2.14.0',date:'2026-06-08',summary:{zh:'v2.14 地城教學：今日詛咒旁！按鈕可查看設定與攻略。',en:'v2.14 dungeon guide: tap ! beside daily curse for settings and tips.'}},{version:'2.13.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.13 硬核經驗值優化：手動戰鬥收益提升、通關獎勵、重複刷圖懲罰放寬。',en:'v2.13 hardcore XP rebalance: better manual combat rewards and clear bonuses.'}},{version:'2.12.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.12 移除掛機系統與無人機戰鬥（含自動地城與伴侶戰鬥）。',en:'v2.12 removed idle system and all drone battle features.'}},{version:'2.11.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.11 極限硬核：崩壞懲罰加重、詞綴更兇、每日詛咒地城（全服同日詛咒、通關額外減崩壞）。',en:'v2.11 ultra-hardcore: stronger decay, harsher modifiers, daily cursed dungeon curse.'}},{version:'2.10.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.10 硬核變數：每趟隨機詞綴與布局、事件格、精英怪；記憶崩壞影響屬性；通關減崩壞、逃脫懲罰、重複刷圖懲罰。',en:'v2.10 hardcore variety: run modifiers, layouts, events, elites; decay hurts stats; clear relief, escape penalty, repeat-run tax.'}},{version:'2.9.2',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.9.2：無人機同伴分潤金幣/經驗/裝備；敵人速度影響回合；掛機預覽反映難度；商店裝備隨挑戰樓層調整。',en:'v2.9.2: drone companion shares gold/XP/gear; enemy SPD affects turns; idle preview by difficulty; shop gear scales with challenge floor.'}},{version:'2.9.1',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.9.1 優化：修復金幣抽幣背包滿、無人機頭目雙倍掉落與卡頓；一鍵裝備可升級替換；逃脫天賦與戰鬥閃避分離；經驗/金幣等級差統一。',en:'v2.9.1: fix gold gacha bag-full loss, drone boss double-drop & UI freeze; equip-all upgrades; escape talent split from dodge; unified level-gap curve.'}},{version:'2.9.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'v2.9 平衡大更新：無人機獎勵下調、金幣等級差懲罰、樓層稀有度加成、荊棘反彈修正、逃脫獨立、速度影響攻速、記憶崩壞放緩、一鍵裝備評分優化。',en:'v2.9 balance overhaul: drone reward nerfs, gold level-gap penalty, floor rarity boost, thorns on hit, separate escape, SPD attack speed, softer memory decay, smarter equip-all.'}},{version:'2.8.16',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'背包石：全難度／無人機可掉，約 200 擊殺 1 顆；60+140 格上限。新增背包空間石。',en:'Bag stones drop in all tiers and drone (~1 per 200 kills); 60+140 cap. New item bag space stone.'}},{version:'2.8.15',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'裝備背包統一原始 60 格；背包石擴充上限為角色等級（Lv.800 最多 +800 顆達 860 格）。',en:'Equip bag unified to 60 base slots; stone expansions cap at character level (Lv.800 + 800 stones = 860 slots).'}},{version:'2.8.14',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'裝備背包石擴充改為僅計算背包石格數，上限為角色等級；舊存檔原始 60 格不計入。',en:'Equip bag stone expansions now count only stone-added slots toward the level cap; legacy 60 base excluded.'}},{version:'2.8.13',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'舊存檔保留 60 格裝備背包擴充值，實際可用格數不受角色等級限制。',en:'Legacy saves keep 60 equip bag slots without character level cap on usable capacity.'}},{version:'2.8.12',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'空間石更名為裝備空間背包石，可於背包使用擴充裝備格數，上限為角色等級。',en:'Space stone renamed to Equip Bag Stone; use from inventory to expand equip bag slots up to character level.'}},{version:'2.8.11',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'點擊「載入更多地城」每次於按鈕上方依可挑戰順序新增 5 個地城等級。',en:'Load more dungeons now appends 5 challenge-order tier entries above the button per click.'}},{version:'2.8.10',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'地城「載入更多地城」按鈕改為永久顯示於面板底部。',en:'Dungeon load-more button is now always visible at the panel bottom.'}},{version:'2.8.9',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'地城列表：已完成地城收合於頂部按鈕，下方僅顯示當前可挑戰地城。',en:'Dungeon list: completed dungeons collapse behind a top toggle; only currently challengeable dungeons show below.'}},{version:'2.8.8',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復掛機系統：合成台與無人機掛機經驗改以地下城趟次經驗比例計算，升級曲線與地城一致。',en:'Idle fix: craft and drone idle XP now scale from dungeon run XP ratios with matching level curves.'}},{version:'2.8.7',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'遊戲日誌統一灰色顯示；地城「載入更多地城」按鈕固定於面板底部，捲動列表時仍可輕鬆點擊。',en:'Game log unified gray styling; dungeon load-more button pinned to the panel bottom while scrolling the list.'}},{version:'2.8.6',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'排行榜等級偵測更精準：合併時保留最高等級、即時注入本地等級，並在等級變動時自動同步。',en:'Leaderboard level detection improved: merge keeps highest level, inject local level in real time, and auto-sync on level changes.'}},{version:'2.8.5',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'手動地城主手／副手攻擊按鈕冷卻由 2 秒調回 1.25 秒。',en:'Manual dungeon main/off-hand attack button cooldown reduced from 2s back to 1.25s.'}},{version:'2.8.4',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'排行榜同步優化：縮短上傳延遲、本地快取即時顯示、漸進載入與開啟時即時更新。',en:'Leaderboard sync optimized: faster uploads, instant cache display, progressive loading, and live updates while open.'}},{version:'2.8.3',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'新增等級排行榜：狀態列設定旁可查看全服前 20 名最高等級玩家。',en:'Level leaderboard: tap Rankings next to Settings to view the top 20 players by level.'}},{version:'2.8.2',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'新版本改為強制更新：偵測到新版本時必須重新整理才能繼續遊戲，無法略過。',en:'Mandatory updates: when a new version is detected you must refresh to continue; skipping is no longer allowed.'}},{version:'2.8.1',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'無人機自動地城擊殺敵人後需等待 3 秒才能鎖定下一目標；手動地城主手／副手攻擊按鈕新增 2 秒點擊冷卻保護。',en:'Drone auto-dungeon waits 3s after a kill before locking the next target; manual dungeon main/off-hand attack buttons have a 2s click cooldown.'}},{version:'2.8.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'100 級後改為幾何級數經驗曲線：升級需求每級遞增 0.87%，地城獎勵每級遞增 0.3%；全勤每天刷地城 10 小時，約需 1.5 年可達 800 級。',en:'Post-Lv.100 geometric XP curve: level requirements +0.87%/level, dungeon rewards +0.3%/level; ~10 h/day dungeons reaches Lv.800 in about 1.5 years.'}},{version:'2.7.1',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'100 級後升級需求顯著提高：101–200 級累積經驗需求約為 1–100 級的三倍；地城經驗獎勵維持原成長，高階升級更具挑戰性。',en:'Post-Lv.100 XP curve steepens: total XP for Lv.101–200 is ~3× Lv.1–100; dungeon XP rewards grow slower, making high-level progression more challenging.'}},{version:'2.7.0',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'大幅平衡玩家經驗值：重構升級曲線，地城獎勵改依樓層難度計算；符合等級的地城約 1 趟升 1 級；刷低層經驗大幅減少；Boss 獎勵改用 Boss 模板。舊存檔自動調整升級需求。',en:'Major XP rebalance: new leveling curve; dungeon rewards scale with floor difficulty (~1 run ≈ 1 level at your tier); farming low floors grants much less XP; boss rewards use boss templates. Existing saves auto-adjust level requirements.'}},{version:'2.6.9',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'雲端同步狀態優化：成功顯示已連線（綠色），失敗顯示已離線（紅色）。',en:'Cloud sync status: success shows Connected (green), failure shows Disconnected (red).'}},{version:'2.6.8',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'裝備可穿戴與地城可進入等級上限調整為角色等級 +50。',en:'Wearable gear and enterable dungeons now allow up to character level +50.'}},{version:'2.6.7',date:'2026-06-07',summary:{zh:'地圖出口（E）新增觸碰保護與離開確認彈窗；修復手動地城戰鬥時經驗條不顯示。',en:'Map exit (E) adds touch protection and leave confirmation; fix XP bar hidden during manual dungeon combat.'}},{version:'2.6.6',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'設定新增「新手教學」按鈕，提供完整雙語入門指南（帳號、地城、戰鬥、裝備、掛機等）。',en:'Settings adds Beginner Guide button with full bilingual tutorial (account, dungeons, combat, gear, idle, etc.).'}},{version:'2.6.5',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'狀態欄下方新增藍色角色經驗條；大廳、手動地城與無人機自動戰鬥時顯示，聊天室隱藏。',en:'Blue player XP bar below status bar; shown in hub, manual dungeon, and drone auto-battle, hidden in chat.'}},{version:'2.6.4',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'戰鬥畫面攻擊力等數值改為四捨五入顯示至小數一位。',en:'Combat stats round to one decimal place in battle UI.'}},{version:'2.6.3',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復手機聊天室開啟後因鍵盤或視窗調整而立即關閉（閃退）。',en:'Fix mobile chat closing immediately when keyboard or viewport resizes.'}},{version:'2.6.2',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復調整文字大小後聊天室版面異常；面板高度隨設定同步。',en:'Fix chat layout after text size changes; panel height syncs with setting.'}},{version:'2.6.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'介面縮放預設與上限改為 1.00x。',en:'UI scale default and max set to 1.00x.'}},{version:'2.6.0',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'聊天室依螢幕尺寸自動調整；修復訊息區滾動、安全區與虛擬鍵盤遮擋。',en:'Chat auto-sizes to viewport; fix message scroll, safe-area, and keyboard overlap.'}},{version:'2.5.9',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復聊天室進入／關閉顯示異常；桌面版改為側欄分頁、手機版覆蓋層狀態同步。',en:'Fix chat open/close layout; desktop sidebar tab and mobile overlay state sync.'}},{version:'2.5.8',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'預設介面與文字放大；文字大小上限調至 2.00x。',en:'Larger default UI/text scale; text size slider max 2.00x.'}},{version:'2.5.7',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復註冊確認彈窗被帳號畫面遮擋導致無反應。',en:'Fix register confirm dialog hidden behind account overlay.'}},{version:'2.5.6',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復聊天個人頁戰鬥屬性、安全性與桌面聊天連線等問題。',en:'Fix chat profile combat stats, security hardening, and desktop chat connect.'}},{version:'2.5.5',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'聊天室顯示玩家等級；長按可檢視其他玩家個人頁面。',en:'Chat shows player level; long-press to view player profiles.'}},{version:'2.5.4',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'無人機掛機上限跟隨玩家等級；修復語言按鈕與狀態欄平均排版。',en:'Drone idle cap follows player level; fix language buttons and even status bar layout.'}},{version:'2.5.3',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'紅色加密武器箱掉落率改為與傳說裝備相同（依難度與 Boss 計算）。',en:'Encrypted weapon crate drop rate now matches legendary equipment drop rate.'}},{version:'2.5.2',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'MTO 品牌更新：載入與帳號標題；註冊玩家名字確認流程。',en:'MTO branding update; register player name confirmation flow.'}},{version:'2.5.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'商店與道具配色：荒坂站金色、晶片店藍色；破解器/武器箱紅色、改名卡藍色。',en:'Shop and item colors: Arasaka gold, chip shop blue; decoder/crate red, rename card blue.'}},{version:'2.5',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'超載晶片商店恢復：破解器與玩家改名卡；荒坂站移除金幣破解器。',en:'Overload chip shop restored with decoder and rename card; removed gold decoder from Arasaka.'}},{version:'2.4',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'獨立聊天後端：Cloudflare Worker + WebSocket，脫離 Gun.js 聊天以降低多玩家卡頓。',en:'Independent chat backend via Cloudflare Worker + WebSocket, replacing Gun.js chat.'}},{version:'2.3',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'效能優化：減少存檔/雲端同步頻率、聊天批次處理、地圖增量渲染，改善多玩家同時在線體驗。',en:'Performance: save/cloud debounce, chat batching, incremental map render.'}},{version:'2.2.2',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'配置 Stripe Live 公鑰（pk_live），正式信用卡充值完整啟用。',en:'Configure Stripe live publishable key for production card recharge.'}},{version:'2.2.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'配置 Stripe Live Payment Links；正式付款可透過 Payment Link 跳轉入帳。',en:'Configure Stripe live Payment Links for production recharge.'}},{version:'2.2',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'充值系統優化為正式付款：Live 模式、伺服器驗證、銀行轉帳改人工核實。',en:'Recharge optimized for live payments: verification API and manual bank review.'}},{version:'2.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'超載晶片充值方案擴充至 HK$648（HK$198/328/448/648），晶片數量依現有比例計算。',en:'Overload chip recharge tiers extended to HK$648 with proportional chip amounts.'}},{version:'2.0',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'新增超載晶片貨幣、充值系統（信用卡/銀行轉帳）與超載晶片商店；頂部狀態欄重新排版。',en:'Add Overload Chip currency, recharge (card/bank), chip shop, and status bar layout.'}},{version:'1.9',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'新增紅色已加密武器箱掉落與解密系統，荒坂貨幣補給站販售高級武器箱破解器。',en:'Add encrypted red weapon crates, decrypt system, and Arasaka decoder shop.'}},{version:'1.8.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'商店系統改為先顯示子商店選單，點擊後才進入對應商店。',en:'Shop system now shows sub-shop menu first before entering a store.'}},{version:'1.8',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'商店改為商店系統，新增分頁：系統裝備補給商店與荒坂貨幣補給站。',en:'Shop renamed to Shop System with equipment supply and Arasaka currency tabs.'}},{version:'1.7',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'新增無人機掛機系統，提升無人機自動戰鬥權限（困難 Lv.400、地獄 Lv.600 解鎖）。',en:'Add drone idle system; unlocks auto drone battle in Hard (Lv.400) and Hell (Lv.600).'}},{version:'1.6',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'裝備名稱全面改為賽博朋克風格，並同步中英文翻譯。',en:'Equipment names updated to cyberpunk theme with synced zh/en translations.'}},{version:'1.5',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復已裝備欄位長按詳情無鎖定按鈕的問題。',en:'Fix missing lock button when viewing equipped items via long-press.'}},{version:'1.4',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復鎖定裝備仍可單件回收的問題，並清理無效鎖定紀錄。',en:'Fix locked equipment still being recyclable individually; prune stale lock IDs on load.'}},{version:'1.3',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'修復裝備部位、屬性、稀有度等同時顯示中英文的問題。',en:'Fix equipment slots, stats, and rarity showing both Chinese and English at once.'}},{version:'1.2',date:'2025-06-07',summary:{zh:'CCO 配色：HP 紅、護盾灰、金幣金、稀有度色彩、白字黑底按鈕。',en:'CCO color scheme: red HP, gray shield, gold coins, rarity colors, white-on-black buttons.'}},{version:'1.1',date:'2025-06-07',summary